    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent so buyers can make an informed decision before visiting. The exterior has sustained significant wear \u2014 you'll find multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and areas where the paint has faded, chipped, or begun to rust. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but is not without issues \u2014 expect that it will require attention and repairs before it can be considered fully reliable for regular use. There may be warning lights present on the dashboard, and some systems may not function as intended. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. We are pricing it accordingly to reflect its current state honestly.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and I want to be upfront about what that means. The exterior shows visible wear beyond typical cosmetic blemishes \u2014 you'll notice scratches, paint chips, and possibly some light surface rust or fading in certain areas. The interior has seen regular use and reflects that, with worn upholstery, scuffs on trim pieces, and general signs of age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may have some deferred maintenance items or minor issues that a buyer should be prepared to address. This is a solid candidate for someone looking for reliable basic transportation or a project vehicle, priced accordingly to reflect its current state. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged so you can make a fully informed decision.",
      "price": 22000.0,
