      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Looking for a budget-friendly project car or bare-bones transportation on a tight budget? This one's for you! We'll be upfront: this vehicle is showing its age and has seen better days \u2014 expect visible wear, some mechanical issues that will need attention, and cosmetic imperfections inside and out. That said, it still has potential for the right hands, whether you're a DIY mechanic looking for a fixer-upper or just need something to get around while you save up. Priced to reflect its current condition, this is a no-surprises deal for a savvy buyer who knows what they're getting into. Come take a look and see if it fits your needs!",
