      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a solid, dependable choice for buyers seeking reliable transportation without the premium price of a mint-condition car. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor cosmetic imperfections such as small surface scratches or light scuffs consistent with normal everyday use. There are no significant dents or major paint issues to report. The interior is clean and functional, showing moderate wear on high-contact areas like the seats and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained to a reasonable standard; all primary systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and electronics \u2014 are in good working order. Buyers can expect a vehicle that is ready to drive without immediate major repairs, though as with any used car in this condition tier, some routine maintenance items may be due. Overall, this is a trustworthy, practical vehicle that offers good value for the price.",
